<lb n="0606b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0606b1101" cb:type="dharani"><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><note n="0606006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梵字真言麗明甲乙四本俱無，今依丙本補載之</note><g ref="#SD-E074"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0606007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（引一）細註【明】</note><note n="0606007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵【大】，唵(引一)【明】</note><app n="0606007"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-CFC5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">阿</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5ED"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">謨</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A464"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">伽</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A65D"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">尾</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A646"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0606008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚧＝盧【明】</note><note n="0606008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚧【大】，盧【明】</note><app n="0606008"><lem wit="【大】">嚧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">盧</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A47C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">左</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">曩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5E5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">摩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A6A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0606009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＝訶【明】</note><note n="0606009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀【大】，訶【明】</note><app n="0606009"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">訶</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-AAC4"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">母捺</cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0606b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0606b13" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>囉</cb:zi><cb:sg><note n="0606010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二合＝二合二【明】，〔二合〕－【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0606010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合【大】，二合二【明】，〔－〕【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0606010"><lem wit="【大】">二合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">二合二</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5E5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">麼</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A54D"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">抳</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5B5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">鉢</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E243"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>納麼</cb:zi><cb:sg>二<note n="0606011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（三）【明】</note><note n="0606011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合三【明】</note><app n="0606011"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">合三</rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E04A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>入嚩</cb:zi><cb:sg>二合</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A64A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">攞</cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0606b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0606b15" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-AABC"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>鉢囉</cb:zi><cb:sg>二合</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A656"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0606b1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">韈【CB】，<g ref="#CB03706"/>【大】</note><app n="0606b1501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.Shao-Yun">韈</lem><rdg wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB03706"/></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-B6C8"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">哆</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5F1"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">野</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E17C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0606012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吽＋（引四）細註【明】，〔引〕細註【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0606012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吽【大】，吽(引四)【明】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->吽(引)【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0606012"><lem wit="【大】">吽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">吽<note place="inline">引四</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">吽<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0606b16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0606b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0606b1701">毘盧遮那如來。為授母陀羅尼<note n="0606013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔印〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0606013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0606013"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三昧耶神
<lb n="0606b18" ed="T"/>通法品。而最為第一。若有過去一切十惡五
<lb n="0606b19" ed="T"/>逆四重諸罪。燼<note n="0606014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">然＝燃【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0606014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">然【大】，燃【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0606014"><lem wit="【大】">然</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">燃</rdg></app>除滅。若有眾生。隨處得
<lb n="0606b20" ed="T"/>聞此大灌頂<note n="0606015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光＋（明）【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0606015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光【大】，光明【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0606015"><lem wit="【大】">光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">光明</rdg></app>真言。<note n="0606016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝一【明】</note><note n="0606016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，一【明】</note><app n="0606016"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">一</rdg></app>三七遍經耳根者。
<lb n="0606b21" ed="T"/>即得除滅一切罪障。<note n="0606017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若諸＝設【明】，若殺【甲】，殺【乙】，教【丙】</note><note n="0606017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若諸【大】，設【明】，若殺【甲】，殺【乙】，教【丙】</note><app n="0606017"><lem wit="【大】">若諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">設</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">若殺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">殺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">教</rdg></app>眾生具造十惡五
<lb n="0606b22" ed="T"/>逆四重諸罪。猶如微塵滿斯世界。身壞命終
<lb n="0606b23" ed="T"/>墮諸惡道。以是真言加持土沙一百八遍。尸
<lb n="0606b24" ed="T"/>陀林中散亡者<note n="0606018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尸＝屍【明】</note><note n="0606018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尸【大】，屍【明】</note><app n="0606018"><lem wit="【大】">尸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">屍</rdg></app>骸上。或散墓上。遇皆散
<lb n="0606b25" ed="T"/>之。彼所亡者。若地獄中若餓鬼中。若修羅中
<lb n="0606b26" ed="T"/>若傍生中。以一切不空如來不空毘盧遮那
<lb n="0606b27" ed="T"/>如來真實<note n="0606019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">本＝大【明】</note><note n="0606019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本【大】，大【明】</note><app n="0606019"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">大</rdg></app>願大灌頂光真言神通威力加
<lb n="0606b28" ed="T"/>持<note n="0606020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沙土＝士沙【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0606020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙土【大】，士沙【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0606020"><lem wit="【大】">沙土</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">士沙</rdg></app>之力。應時即得光明<note n="0606021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">及身＝身及【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0606021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及身【大】，身及【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0606021"><lem wit="【大】">及身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">身及</rdg></app>除諸罪
<lb n="0606b29" ed="T"/>報捨所苦身。往於西方極樂國土。蓮華化生
<pb n="0606c" xml:id="T19.1002.0606c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0606c01" ed="T"/>乃至菩提更不墮落。復有眾生連年累月。痿
<lb n="0606c02" ed="T"/>黃疾惱苦楚萬端。是病人者先世業報。以是
<lb n="0606c03" ed="T"/>真言於病者前。一二三日每日高聲誦此真
<lb n="0606c04" ed="T"/>言一千八十遍。則得除滅宿業病障。若為鬼
<lb n="0606c05" ed="T"/>嬈魂識悶亂失音不語。持真言者加持手一
<lb n="0606c06" ed="T"/>百八遍。摩捫頭面。以手按於心上額上。加持
<lb n="0606c07" ed="T"/>一千八十遍。則得除差。摩訶迦羅神作病惱
<lb n="0606c08" ed="T"/>者。亦能治遣。若諸鬼神魍魎之病。加持五色
<lb n="0606c09" ed="T"/>線索。一百<note n="0606022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">八＋（遍）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0606022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八【大】，八遍【校異-乙】</note><app n="0606022"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">八遍</rdg></app>結。繫其病者腰臂<note n="0606023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">項＝頂【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0606023" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->項【大】＊，頂【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0606023"><lem wit="【大】">項</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">頂</rdg></app>上。則便
<lb n="0606c10" ed="T"/>除差。若諸瘧病。加持白線索一百八結。繫頭
<lb n="0606c11" ed="T"/>項上。及加持衣著。即令除差。若加持石<note n="0606024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">菖＝昌【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0606024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菖【大】，昌【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0606024"><lem wit="【大】">菖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">昌</rdg></app>
<lb n="0606c12" ed="T"/>蒲一千八十遍。<note n="0606025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">含＝捨【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0606025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">含【大】，捨【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0606025"><lem wit="【大】">含</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">捨</rdg></app>之與他相對談論。則勝他
<lb n="0606c13" ed="T"/>伏。若以胡椒多誐囉香。青木香小柏<note n="0606026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">檀＝橿【丙】</note><note n="0606026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">檀【大】，橿【丙】</note><app n="0606026"><lem wit="【大】">檀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">橿</rdg></app>黃。
<lb n="0606c14" ed="T"/>囉娑<note n="0606027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惹＝若【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0606027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惹【大】，若【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0606027"><lem wit="【大】">惹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">若</rdg></app>娜<note place="inline"><note n="0606028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唐＝此【明】</note><note n="0606028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唐【大】，此【明】</note><app n="0606028"><lem wit="【大】">唐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">此</rdg></app>言小栢汁</note>等數末。治水丸如棗。加持
<lb n="0606c15" ed="T"/>十萬遍。便當陰乾。若患一切<note n="0606029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鬼神病＝鬼病神病【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0606029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鬼神病【大】，鬼病神病【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0606029"><lem wit="【大】">鬼神病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">鬼病神病</rdg></app>種種瘧
<lb n="0606c16" ed="T"/>病。或毒藥中或失音者。<note n="0606030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（皆）＋當【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0606030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，皆當【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0606030"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">皆當</rdg></app>以藥和水研之。
<lb n="0606c17" ed="T"/>加持一百八遍。<note n="0606031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">數＝散【乙】</note><note n="0606031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">數【大】，散【乙】</note><app n="0606031"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">散</rdg></app>點兩眼額上心上。當怒加
<lb n="0606c18" ed="T"/>持。則便除<note n="0606032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">差＝若【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0606032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差【大】，若【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0606032"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">若</rdg></app>。作病鬼神若不放捨。即當頭
<lb n="0606c19" ed="T"/>破如阿梨樹枝。若諸毒蟲蛇蝎螫者。以藥塗
<lb n="0606c20" ed="T"/><note n="0606033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眼＝服ィ【甲】</note><note n="0606033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眼【大】，服【校異-甲】</note><app n="0606033"><lem wit="【大】">眼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">服</rdg></app>即便除差。</p>
<lb n="0606c21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0606c2101">又法以新米𡅄羅。澡浴清淨著淨衣服已。以
<lb n="0606c22" ed="T"/>藥和水研。加持一百八遍點米𡅄羅眼中。奮
<lb n="0606c23" ed="T"/>怒加持一千八十遍。則便起坐所<note n="0606034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">問＝問【丙】</note><note n="0606034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">問【大】，問【丙】</note><app n="0606034"><lem wit="【大】">問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">問</rdg></app>皆答。
<pb n="0607a" xml:id="T19.1002.0607a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0607a01" ed="T"/><note n="0607001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（若）＋欲【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0607001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲【大】，若欲【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0607001"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">若欲</rdg></app>放者。加持白芥子水二十一遍。散米𡅄羅
<lb n="0607a02" ed="T"/>上。即便如舊。若為貴人相請喚者。以藥點眼
<lb n="0607a03" ed="T"/>當往見之。則相賓敬。</p>
<lb n="0607a04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>不空羂索毘盧遮那佛大灌頂光真言<app type="star" corresp="#0606002"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">經</rdg></app><note n="0607002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本奧書曰長寬三年三月十九日於勸修寺西明院書了，乙本奧書曰仁安二年閏七月十二日書寫了一交了</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
